('Readwise', 'readwise', 'https://readwise.io', '', 'Okuduklarınızı unutmamanızı sağlayan, her platformla entegre kütüphane.', 'Readwise makes it easy to revisit and learn from your e-book & article highlights.', 'Knowledge', '["reading", "library", "notes"]', 'paid', 'tr', 1, 1, 19500),
