('Claude', 'claude', 'https://claude.ai', '', 'Anthropic tarafından geliştirilen güvenli ve yetenekli yapay zeka asistanı.', 'Claude is a next-generation AI assistant based on Anthropic’s research into training helpful, honest, and harmless AI systems.', 'AI Assistant', '["chat", "anthropic", "llm"]', 'freemium', 'tr', 0, 1, 85000),
